- "The ball flies the highest and most frequently" refers to a high average number of goals scored per match;
- "The vast stadium of soccer" is a metaphor for the world of soccer leagues;
- "More than 50 matches played" is a condition to ensure the data is statistically significant.

- League ID 1 refers to a specific league in the database;
- City A is a location where the teams are based;
- Matches played refers to the number of matches a team has participated in within the league.

